    "To enhance the capability of LLMs on zero-shot IE tasks that necessitate structured outputs, our prompting pipeline integrates three key components, as depicted in Figure 1: 1) free-form response generation, which prompts LLMs to identify the required information from the provided context without imposing any syntactic or structural constraints on the result; 2) answer clean-",
